---
title: Fiery Mexican Pork Meatballs & Corn Rice with Bacon-Tomato Salsa & Yoghurt
description: Pork meatballs are lighting a fire of excitement with spices on popping corn rice. The secret to add that spark is a tomato salsa with golden bacon. It’s a firework of flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/657165b938e51a4a51a2ff77-c7d8a9b8.jpeg
